   Application Search

     * Wireless Telecommunications Bureau's Universal Licensing System
       (ULS)
       Applications for public safety, amateur radio, aviation, and
       private wireless services
     * Mass Media Bureau's CDBS Public Access System
       Applications for AM & FM radio, TV, Low-Power TV, and DTV broadcast
       licenses
     * Mass Media Bureau's BLS Public Access System
       Applications for Multipoint Distribution System (MDS) and
       Instructional Television Fixed Service (ITFS)stations

